ED_Title: Comprehensive  review of the whole question of peacekeeping operations in all their aspects
ED_DecisionText: At its 47th plenary meeting, on 13 December 2019, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee) (A/74/411).
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/74/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
